    {
      "beat_id": "B14",
      "t_start": 127.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 14.0,
      "narration_text": "A student checks every possible assignment. A1 plus one, A2 minus one. They write out all four B1, B2 rows. Every time: S equals plus or minus two. They try A1 plus one, A2 plus one. Same result. Every combination, always two. The bound is not a statistical limit — it is a constant.",
      "shot": {
